Dialogue: 10,0:00:01.46,0:00:04.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dalam situasi ini, hubungan militer\Ndan Kuil pasti sangatlah kuat.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:04.51,0:00:09.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hubungan itu pasti bisa mengantar\Numat manusia pada kemenangan.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:09.75,0:00:11.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Paman.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:12.90,0:00:16.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku kagum pada dedikasimu.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:16.51,0:00:16.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:19.08,0:00:22.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Semoga Mahaeyzel yang suci memberkatimu.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:24.86,0:00:27.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nah, mari putar keadaan.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:36.72,0:00:38.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Paman!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:38.25,0:00:39.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:39.35,0:00:42.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku ingin dapatkan informasi\Nyang lebih akurat.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:42.81,0:00:45.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Orang yang melihat faerie menyusup
Dialogue: 10,0:00:45.41,0:00:46.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,berasal dari kompi mana?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:46.90,0:00:50.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pasukan pertahanan Kota Ioff unit 7110.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:50.61,0:00:55.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada beberapa penyintas,\Ntapi mereka tak bisa bicara sekarang.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:56.71,0:00:58.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mengerti.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:58.58,0:01:00.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sampai nanti.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:08.15,0:01:11.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sudah mengamankan jalur penyusupan.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:11.31,0:01:14.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Waktunya kembali jalankan tugasku.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:24.91,0:01:26.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bersiap menyerang balik!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:26.78,0:01:30.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kapten Unit Penembak Jitu Siena,\Ntolong hambat gerakan mereka.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:30.27,0:01:32.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kapten Kavaleri Zoffleck,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:32.41,0:01:34.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,kami sudah siap.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:35.00,0:01:36.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Semuanya!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:36.40,0:01:37.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mulai menembak!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:42.11,0:01:43.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Luar biasa!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:46.96,0:01:49.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sekarang. Pecah formasi mereka!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:55.44,0:01:56.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ikuti aku!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:56.48,0:01:58.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bereskan faerie yang tak tertembak!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:58.45,0:01:59.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cepat taklukkan!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:59.95,0:02:00.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baik!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:03.52,0:02:04.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lumayan, lah.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:05.06,0:02:08.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mari serahkan wilayah ini\Nkepada para Kesatria Suci.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:09.02,0:02:13.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita harus segera melacak\Nkeberadaan Raja Iblis Spriggan.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:56.21,0:03:57.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tatsuya, maju!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:25.55,0:04:26.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu faerie jenis baru?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:26.71,0:04:27.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bentuk manusia, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.58,0:04:28.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa mereka bermusuhan?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.85,0:04:30.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kami manusia!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:30.41,0:04:31.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cepat buka!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:32.08,0:04:33.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Manusia...?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.51,0:04:36.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Segel suci itu...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.38,0:04:37.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pahlawan terpidana?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.64,0:04:38.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cepat!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.21,0:04:41.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Para faerie akan memanggil bantuan!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.55,0:04:43.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian semua cari mati, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.05,0:04:47.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian takkan bertahan lama\Njika diam di dalam sana!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.18,0:04:49.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Xylo, jangan seperti itu!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.11,0:04:52.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Warga... sekalian!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.41,0:04:57.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Warga sekalian!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.95,0:04:59.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku Dewi Teoritta.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.91,0:05:01.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku datang untuk menyelamatkan kalian.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:01.91,0:05:03.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tolong ikuti arahan kami!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.92,0:05:06.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia benar, warga sekalian!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:06.04,0:05:08.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Gudang ini berada dalam bahaya.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:09.11,0:05:11.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namun, kalian bisa tenang.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:11.81,0:05:14.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,"Dewi" Pedang yang Bersinar, Nona Teoritta
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.99,0:05:18.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan "Elang Gemuruh Petir",\NXylo Forbartz telah tiba!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.26,0:05:20.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nona "Dewi"?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.40,0:05:21.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Elang Gemuruh Petir itu...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.88,0:05:22.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan-jangan...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:23.41,0:05:25.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Sembarangan saja.\N- Ups.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.51,0:05:27.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Siapa yang kau panggil Elang Gemuruh Petir?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:27.61,0:05:30.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Rumornya sampai ke dalam sel penjara, lo.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.55,0:05:33.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Konon, kau dikenal dengan julukan itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.15,0:05:34.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan bercanda, kau...!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:34.25,0:05:34.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Xylo!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:34.91,0:05:36.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa yang engkau permasalahkan?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.59,0:05:40.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dewi Pedang yang Bersinar\Ndan "Elang Gemuruh Petir".
Dialogue: 10,0:05:41.46,0:05:44.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukankah itu nama yang cocok\Nuntuk dua pahlawan yang perkasa...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:58.64,0:06:00.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita buat mereka siap bertarung juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.57,0:06:05.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Rhyno, kau ajari mereka\Ncara menggunakan tongkat petir.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.24,0:06:07.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, serahkan padaku.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:07.55,0:06:10.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan menjawab ekspektasi Kawan Xylo.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:10.62,0:06:14.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi aku ingin mendiskusikan\Nsesuatu denganmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.34,0:06:15.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hah?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.33,0:06:19.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tolong tentukan urutan kematian warga sipil.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:19.06,0:06:20.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau...!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.51,0:06:23.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kurasa kita bisa mulai dari orang tua renta.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:23.52,0:06:26.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mereka sudah hidup lebih lama\Ndibandingkan anak-anak.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.95,0:06:29.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukankah adil jika mereka mati lebih...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.05,0:06:33.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau kira aku akan menjawab,\N"Ah, ide bagus, tuh", pada saranmu, hah?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:33.85,0:06:36.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau sedang mempermasalahkan moralitas, kah?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.01,0:06:42.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita harus usahakan yang terbaik\Nhingga detik-detik paling akhir.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.49,0:06:46.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Setelah itu,\Nbaru kita pikirkan pengorbanan warga sipil.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:52.51,0:06:54.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bala bantuannya keburu datang.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.45,0:06:57.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Xylo, kau belum selesai juga?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:57.75,0:06:59.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dasar lelet.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.98,0:07:03.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya aku lagi yang menang.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.61,0:07:17.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih, Kawan Jayce, Kawan Neely.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:17.85,0:07:21.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Izinkan aku mewakili para pengungsi\Nmengucapkan terima kasih.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.42,0:07:22.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berisik kau, dasar dungu.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:23.77,0:07:26.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dotta, di mana targetku selanjutnya?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:26.36,0:07:28.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah, mengenai itu...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:28.09,0:07:29.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini lumayan gawat!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:29.55,0:07:32.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku lihat pria berzirah hitam\Ndi menara merah.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.63,0:07:36.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Artileri yang waktu itu, ya, Neely!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.61,0:07:43.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Peluru pelacak, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.29,0:07:45.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, mereka takkan bisa bantu kita.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.57,0:07:49.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Rhyno, aku dan Teoritta\Nakan menyerang Tui Jia.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.85,0:07:53.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau dan Tatsuya harus lindungi gudang\Nmeski nyawa taruhannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:53.15,0:07:58.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tentu saja. Mari gabungkan kekuatan\Nuntuk melewati cobaan yang sulit ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.21,0:08:00.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena di detik kalian menolakku,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.35,0:08:03.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku akan kehilangan tempat\Nuntuk kembali di dunia ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.45,0:08:04.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak jelas.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:04.91,0:08:06.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bikin merinding saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.58,0:08:12.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baiklah.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:15.18,0:08:19.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nah, mari perlihatkan ikatan\Nserta keberanian kita.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.13,0:08:21.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Waktunya bertarung.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:21.98,0:08:25.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Demi kemenangan dan perdamaian umat manusia!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:26.11,0:08:29.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Wah, ini kejutan.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.32,0:08:33.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kesatria Naga itu hebat juga\Nkarena bisa menghindari yang tadi.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:33.20,0:08:37.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita bisa repot jika naga itu\Nbergerak dengan bebas.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:37.45,0:08:41.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Paus Logam, hentikan mereka.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.05,0:08:44.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu,\Nkau atasi orang yang mendekati kita.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.91,0:08:48.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Artileri itu rentan saat didekati musuh.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:48.58,0:08:51.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah begitu,\Nlawannya "Pembunuh Dewi", 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:51.95,0:08:53.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar, dia kuat.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.95,0:08:55.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku menghormatinya.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:56.59,0:08:59.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau aneh juga, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:59.58,0:09:04.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kukira Malapetaka Raja Iblis\Nadalah sosok yang sangat keji.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.55,0:09:08.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Banyak yang seperti itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.02,0:09:10.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi aku berbeda.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:10.35,0:09:12.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak benci manusia.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.91,0:09:17.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku justru menghormati\Nmereka karena akan kubinasakan.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.31,0:09:21.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maka dari itu pula,\Naku tak menyukai Spriggan.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.99,0:09:24.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia kurang rasa hormat.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:25.11,0:09:31.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hanya Raja yang mampu memahami pola pikirku.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.01,0:09:34.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Raja? Raja Iblis juga punya raja, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.93,0:09:38.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah, aku terlalu banyak bicara.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.35,0:09:40.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Obrolan kita selesai.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:40.51,0:09:43.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, aku juga takkan ikut campur.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.21,0:09:44.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dalam industri ini,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:44.46,0:09:47.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,orang yang tahu terlalu banyak akan mati\Ndengan mengenaskan.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:51.52,0:09:53.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,"Pembunuh Dewi" segera tiba.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.49,0:09:57.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak membenci manusia sepertinya,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.25,0:10:01.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi perlu kubunuh.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:02.91,0:10:06.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Semuanya demi Raja.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.42,0:10:13.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Komandan Kivia!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.39,0:10:16.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kami berhasil mengambil alih\Narea bangunan legislatif.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:16.62,0:10:18.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa operasi selanjutnya?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.15,0:10:24.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Komandan Kivia?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.38,0:10:29.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf, kuserahkan komando di lapangan\Nkepada masing-masing kapten.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.38,0:10:34.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku harus mengurus hal lain.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:37.75,0:10:40.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf, untuk detailnya...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:40.37,0:10:41.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak apa-apa.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:43.25,0:10:47.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sudah putuskan untuk patuh kepadamu,\Napa pun yang terjadi.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.58,0:10:52.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di Couvenge juga sama.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.61,0:10:57.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena Komandan Kivia-lah\Nyang mengajari aku cara menggenggam pedang.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:00.51,0:11:02.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan kembali ke posku.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:03.75,0:11:05.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Rajit.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:05.14,0:11:06.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.78,0:11:12.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya aku perlu ceritakan kepadamu.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.25,0:11:16.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Untuk berjaga-jaga\Nbila terjadi sesuatu padaku.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:22.75,0:11:25.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kawan Xylo, aku sudah siap di posisi.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:25.71,0:11:27.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Orang-orang di gudang baik-baik saja, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.76,0:11:31.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar, tak ada masalah di sini.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.33,0:11:33.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Toh Kawan Tatsuya ada di sini.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:36.01,0:11:39.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Siapa sangka\Ndia juga menguasai tongkat petir.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.51,0:11:44.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita beruntung dia memihak umat manusia.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:44.72,0:11:47.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita harus berterima kasih padanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:47.81,0:11:50.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Venetim, Tsav masih lama?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:50.61,0:11:52.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, masih butuh waktu.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:52.85,0:11:56.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena ada faerie\Nyang muncul di area tengah kota.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.40,0:11:59.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Teoritta, kau siap?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.95,0:12:01.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, mari berangkat.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:01.60,0:12:03.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Demi umat manusia!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.25,0:12:06.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mungkin kita berdua akan tumbang di sini.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.75,0:12:10.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berbeda denganku, nyawamu hanya ada satu.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.38,0:12:15.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Engkau pun akan kehilangan ingatan\Nsaat tewas,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:15.98,0:12:18.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan melupakan banyak kenangan, bukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:19.10,0:12:22.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan melindungi ingatanmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:23.25,0:12:26.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sedangkan nyawaku,\Nbiar engkau yang lindungi.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:27.78,0:12:31.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berkorban nyawa\Nuntuk orang lain sangat bodoh.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:32.14,0:12:33.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Meski begitu,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:33.31,0:12:34.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku akan lakukan!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:36.71,0:12:38.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita mulai, Teoritta!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.41,0:12:45.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita selesaikan sebelum fajar\Ndan sarapan yang banyak!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.75,0:12:48.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Roti yang baru dipanggang\Ndengan Zeff Butter!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.15,0:12:49.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sup bawang bombai juga!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.81,0:12:51.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lengkap dengan bakon\Nyang digoreng hingga matang!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:51.98,0:12:54.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalimat mengharukan\Nyang benar-benar khas "Dewi"!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.91,0:12:56.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku jadi lapar!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:02.73,0:13:03.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak apa-apa.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:03.87,0:13:06.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Neely jauh lebih cepat\Ndibandingkan peluru itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:06.26,0:13:08.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita tak mungkin kena.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:09.05,0:13:12.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa kau lambat sekali, Xylo?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:14.45,0:13:16.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yang benar saja...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:18.01,0:13:20.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kesatriaku, jalan lain...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:20.52,0:13:21.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak ada.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:22.61,0:13:25.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita terpaksa terobos di sini!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:34.29,0:13:36.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima ini!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:37.46,0:13:38.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku juga!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.36,0:13:46.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Teoritta, kita terobos sekarang!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:50.35,0:13:51.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Keras kepala.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:55.85,0:13:57.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Xylo.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:57.11,0:13:58.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak apa-apa.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:58.78,0:14:00.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau curang juga, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:00.86,0:14:02.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Memang seperti inilah pekerjaanku.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:04.94,0:14:07.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kali ini, aku akan hadapi dengan serius!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:11.08,0:14:13.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Paus Logam, kita kepung mereka!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.16,0:14:15.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan sampai kena aku!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:16.24,0:14:17.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sibuk banget, dah!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.92,0:14:20.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Xylo, biar aku...!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.06,0:14:25.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di mana dia?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:32.61,0:14:33.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mati kau!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.95,0:14:36.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Teoritta, sekarang!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.22,0:14:46.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei, kau bisa lihat ini, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:46.98,0:14:47.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bisa!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:48.36,0:14:50.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sekarang jauh lebih mudah.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:51.24,0:14:52.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Neely!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.16,0:14:56.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selamat tinggal!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:04.21,0:15:05.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sial!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:05.25,0:15:07.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku pasti sial kalau melihat ke arah lain.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:07.95,0:15:10.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Rhyno, kau sudah bisa membidik, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:10.81,0:15:12.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tentu.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:12.51,0:15:16.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Perhitunganku sudah selesai,\Nperhatian lawan pun teralihkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.58,0:15:19.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bisa kuhancurkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:22.19,0:15:23.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada tembakan?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.98,0:15:30.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yang benar saja...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:33.01,0:15:36.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tembakan seperti itu... tak mung...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:42.98,0:15:45.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku harus buat alasan seperti apa...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:46.63,0:15:48.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kesatriaku, menaranya...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:48.81,0:15:50.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, itu bagian dari rencanaku.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:51.19,0:15:52.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita lompat!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:56.85,0:15:58.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia datang.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:05.38,0:16:07.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini kedua kalinya kau meminta tolong.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.85,0:16:12.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau memperlakukanku dari Penghuni Malam\Nsebagai agen intelijen?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.95,0:16:17.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Padahal aku sudah sibuk melacak\Nkeberadaan Raja Iblis Spriggan.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.18,0:16:21.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak punya waktu untuk pilih-pilih lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:21.25,0:16:22.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kumohon!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:22.98,0:16:24.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak peduli berapa bayarannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:24.75,0:16:26.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saat kenyataannya sudah terbukti nanti...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:26.40,0:16:27.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mengerti.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.71,0:16:33.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kami akan laporkan hasilnya sebelum fajar.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:35.61,0:16:37.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku berutang padamu.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.85,0:16:42.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Semuanya demi Xylo,\Nsuami keluarga Mastibolt.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:45.71,0:16:47.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selain itu,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:47.19,0:16:50.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku takkan rugi\Njika membiarkan Kesatria Suci
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.25,0:16:52.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,berutang budi padaku.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.31,0:16:54.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sampai nanti.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:02.86,0:17:03.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sekarang!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:03.71,0:17:05.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tembak!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:07.93,0:17:09.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Raja!\N- Pasukan kedua, ke depan!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:09.71,0:17:11.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Gelombang selanjutnya datang!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:11.00,0:17:13.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selanjutnya kawanan Bogie.\NJauh lebih sulit!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.98,0:17:16.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kayaknya kita kabur saja dari sini, deh?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:16.01,0:17:16.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak bisa!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:17.38,0:17:19.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jika kau turun\Ndari sana barang satu langkah,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.51,0:17:20.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,kau akan dapat eksekusi mati.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:21.51,0:17:23.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Manfaatkan ketajaman matamu!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:23.78,0:17:26.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau kira untuk apa aku meminjamkan\Ntongkat petir Tsav padamu?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:28.81,0:17:30.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak bisa pakai benda seberat ini!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:31.18,0:17:33.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Setidaknya lindungi tempat ini sampai mati!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.75,0:17:35.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebentar lagi Tsav akan tiba!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:35.65,0:17:38.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa dia benar-benar akan datang?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.01,0:17:39.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau aku, sih, pasti kabur.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:39.78,0:17:40.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pasti!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.95,0:17:43.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia memang penjahat,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:43.01,0:17:45.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi bukan penjahat yang akan kabur\Ndalam kondisi seperti ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:45.91,0:17:50.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu... Kok kesannya kayak menyindir halus\Nkalau aku penjahat yang tidak baik, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:50.38,0:17:52.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku pernah berpikir seperti itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:52.78,0:17:57.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namun, kebodohanmu\Nterkadang membawakan mukjizat.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:57.58,0:18:00.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tentu saja, berdasarkan komentar\Nkomandan tertinggi pasukanku!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:00.80,0:18:03.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sekarang, kita hanya bisa\Nmenunggu kemenangan.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:03.50,0:18:05.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Percaya dan menunggu bawahannya
Dialogue: 10,0:18:05.85,0:18:08.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,adalah tanggung jawab\Nyang harus dipenuhi seorang raja.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.98,0:18:28.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Refleks yang luar biasa.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.85,0:18:32.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau melebihi ekspektasiku,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.25,0:18:34.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Xylo Forbartz.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:39.05,0:18:40.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Darah, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:40.45,0:18:43.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau lawan yang benar-benar kuat.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:46.31,0:18:51.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bila ada kesempatan, meski sangat kecil,\Nuntuk membunuh "Dewi"...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:51.71,0:18:55.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku harus mencobanya!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:04.61,0:19:06.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak bisa mendekat.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:06.15,0:19:08.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jayce, bantu aku!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:08.15,0:19:11.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak bisa melihat jelas\Nkarena kabut darah dan debu.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:11.82,0:19:14.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau mau ikut aku bakar?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:14.38,0:19:16.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mana mungkin...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:18.01,0:19:20.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Rhyno, kenapa kau malah bengong di sana?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:20.75,0:19:21.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tembak yang banyak!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:21.91,0:19:24.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sayangnya aku juga\Ntak bisa melihat dengan jelas.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:24.98,0:19:27.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku harus hitung ulang dari awal.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:27.05,0:19:28.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi tak apa-apa.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:28.81,0:19:31.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Toh menaranya pasti roboh.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:31.19,0:19:34.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sial. Mereka semua tak berguna!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:34.86,0:19:37.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya sudahlah. Aku sendiri saja!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.79,0:19:58.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bajingan...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:59.77,0:20:00.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Xylo!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:00.91,0:20:02.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Gerakannya sudah kuhentikan.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:02.97,0:20:04.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan bunuh
Dialogue: 10,0:20:05.01,0:20:06.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,sekarang juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:07.01,0:20:09.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,"Dewi" Teoritta.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:10.71,0:20:17.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau harus kubunuh apa pun yang terjadi.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:21.30,0:20:22.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Teoritta.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:22.61,0:20:24.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan menunjukkan wajah seperti itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.31,0:20:30.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Percayalah pada kesatriamu,\Ndan bersikaplah sok jago!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:31.65,0:20:35.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Percayalah kalau aku tak terkalahkan!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:36.13,0:20:38.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Xylo Forbartz!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:01.15,0:21:02.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.38,0:21:05.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Waktumu habis, Boojum.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:09.71,0:21:11.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitu, ya...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:12.05,0:21:14.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namun, masih belum...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:15.81,0:21:17.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Masih belum!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:22.61,0:21:23.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Xylo, lukamu...!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:23.59,0:21:25.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Abaikan saja!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.02,0:21:40.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagus.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.78,0:21:52.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dulu, aku juga pernah bertarung\Nseperti sekarang.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:54.45,0:21:55.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sekali lagi...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:04.48,0:22:06.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sampai kapan tubuhku mampu bertahan?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:05.54,0:22:06.80,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana dengan stamina Teoritta?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:06.39,0:22:07.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selanjutnya penentuan menang dan kalah.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:07.76,0:22:08.91,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Baca gerakan Boojum.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:08.91,0:22:09.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak boleh kalah.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:09.68,0:22:10.96,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Masa bodoh dengan pahlawan.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:10.96,0:22:12.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Demi mereka...!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:13.56,0:22:15.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kali ini, aku pasti
Dialogue: 10,0:22:17.81,0:22:19.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,berhasil!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:19.85,0:22:21.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagus.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:28.61,0:22:31.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Luar biasa, Xylo Forbartz.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:32.45,0:22:36.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau pasti bisa menjadi\Npenyair pahlawan yang hebat.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:37.61,0:22:40.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau bisa,\Naku ingin menyaksikan hal itu terjadi...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:41.08,0:22:44.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namun, justru karena itu pula,
Dialogue: 10,0:22:44.51,0:22:47.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku harus mengalahkanmu\Ndengan sekuat tenaga!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:48.54,0:22:49.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pusaran Darah.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:53.94,0:22:56.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kesatriaku, aku takkan maafkan\Nbila kau gagal!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:56.99,0:22:57.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oke!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:00.47,0:23:03.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita akhiri dengan ini!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:07.85,0:23:09.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Satu serangan lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:10.91,0:23:12.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau bisa, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:12.70,0:23:16.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tentu. Kau juga harus bisa!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:16.16,0:23:18.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Walau harus memaksakan diri!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:20.34,0:23:21.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sombong sekali!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:22.57,0:23:26.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau harus mati demi rajaku!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:36.47,0:23:39.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Xylo Forbartz!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:44.77,0:23:45.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Inilah...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:45.98,0:23:49.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pedang Suci yang mengakhiri dunia ini, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:54.58,0:23:59.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tiada lawan yang tak dapat\NPedang Suci binasakan.
